  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a 10-inch clay or ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add coconut oil to the tagine and swirl it to coat the bottom.",
    "Add the grated ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute, until softened.",
    "Add the chopped beetroot and cook for 5 minutes, until slightly tender.",
    "Add the dark brown soft sugar, gochujang, and 1/4 cup of water to the tagine.",
    "Stir to combine and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and cook, covered, for 20 minutes, or until the beetroot is tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Garnish with sesame seeds and chopped green onions.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature."
  ],
